    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Lifeweaver heals from range with Healing Blossom, using Life Grip to pull an endangered ally to safety and Petal Platform to control high ground and sightlines for his team.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Life Grip can be baited or used on the wrong target under pressure, and once it&#39;s on cooldown he has no other hard save for a teammate about to die.</p>\n"
